@startuml
title Error Normalization (After)
skinparam backgroundColor #F8FAFD
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #37474F
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas

actor "SDK Consumer" as Consumer #B2EBF2
component "AthenaGatewayError" as GatewayError #FFCCBC
component "normalizeAthenaError()" as Normalize #FFE082
component "AthenaErrorCode constants" as ErrorCode #C5E1A5
component "AthenaErrorCategory constants" as ErrorCategory #D1C4E9
component "AthenaErrorKind constants" as ErrorKind #FFF59D
component "AthenaError class" as AthenaErrorClass #B3E5FC
component "Retry policy helper" as RetryPolicy #AED581

GatewayError --> Normalize : source failures
Normalize --> ErrorKind : classify by status/message
Normalize --> ErrorCode : map to machine code
Normalize --> ErrorCategory : map to category
Normalize --> RetryPolicy : derive retryable
Normalize --> Consumer : normalized envelope
Consumer --> AthenaErrorClass : optional typed error object

note right of Normalize
Backward compatible helper contract retained,
with added code/category/retryable metadata.
end note
@enduml
